\c 21
\s Jobho anoti, vakaipa vanenge vanofara havo vasingatambudzwi naMwari, asi vachatongwa panguva inouya
\p
\v 1 Ipapo Jobho akapindura, akati:
\p
\v 2 Inzwai zvakanaka kutaura kwangu; munyaradzwe nazvo.
\v 3 Ndiregei, nditaurewo; kana ndapedza kutaura, mungandiseka henyu.
\v 4 Kana ndirini, ndinochema kuvanhu here? Ndingaregereiko kupera moyo?
\v 5 Nditarirei, mushamiswe, muise ruoko rwenyu pamuromo.
\v 6 Kunyange ndozvirangarira ndinotambudzika, kutya kukuru kunobata nyama yangu.
\p
\v 7 Vakaipa vanoraramireiko, vachikwegura nokuwedzerwa simba here?
\v 8 Vana vavo vanosimbiswa pamwe chete navo pamberi pavo, navazukuru vavo vachizviona nameso avo.
\v 9 Dzimba dzavo dzinorugare, hadzityiswi, uye shamhu yaMwari haigari ichivarova.
\v 10 Hando yavo inoberekesa, isingakoni, mhou yavo inobereka, isingasvodzi.
\v 11 Vanobudisa pwere dzavo seboka ramakwai; vana vavo vanotamba.
\v 12 Vanoimba vachiridzirwa ngoma nembira, vanofara vachiridzirwa nyere.
\v 13 Vanopedza mazuva avo vachifara, vanoburukira kuSheori kamwe-kamwe.
\v 14 Kunyange zvakadaro vanoti kuna Mwari, ibvai kwatiri; nokuti hatidi kuziva nzira dzenyu.
\v 15 Iye Wemasimbaose ndianiko, kuti timushumire? Tichabatsirwa neiko kana tikakumbirisa kwaari?
\v 16 Tarirai, kufara kwavo hakuzi mumaoko avo; mano avakaipa ari kure neni.
\p
\v 17 Ko mwenje wavakaipa unodzimwa kangani? Njodzi yavo inovavinga kanganiko? Mwari anovapavhurira kutambudzika pakutsamwa kwake kanganiko?
\v 18 Vanotongofanana namakoto anopepereswa nemhepo here? Nehundi inotorwa nedutu remhepo?
\v 19 Imwi munoti: Mwari anochengetera vana vake zvakaipa. Ngaamutsive iye amene, azvizive.
\v 20 Meso ake amene ngaaone kuparadzwa kwake, iye ngaamwe kutsamwa koWemasimbaose.
\v 21 Nokuti achava nehanya yeiko neimba yake kana aenda, kana kuwanda kwemwedzi yake kwatapudzwa.
\p
\v 22 Ndianiko angadzidzisa Mwari kuziva, zvaari iye anotonga vari kumusoro?
\v 23 Umwe anofa achine simba rake rese, akafara chose anorugare.
\v 24 Mazamu ake azere nomukaka, mwongo wamapfupa ake wakanyorova.
\v 25 Umwe anofa ane shungu dzomoyo, asina kutongoravira zvakanaka.
\v 26 Vanorara pasi pamwe chete paguruva, honye dzinovafukidza vese.
\p
\v 27 Tarirai ndinoziva kufunga kwenyu, namano akaipa amunondifungira.
\v 28 Nokuti munoti, imba yomuchinda iripiko? Tende raigarwa nowakaipa riripiko?
\v 29 Hamuna kubvunza here vanofamba nenzira? Hamuzivi zviratidzo zvavo here?
\v 30 Kuti munhu wakaipa anoregerwa pazuva renjodzi, pazuva rokutsamwa kukuru vanobviswa.
\v 31 Ndianiko angamuzivisa mufambiro wake pachena? Ndiani achamutsiva zvaakaita here?
\v 32 Zvino anotakurirwa kuhwiro, kurindwe churu \add chake\add*.
\v 33 Mavhinga omupata achamunakira, vanhu vese vachamutevera, sezvaakatungamirirwa navasingaverengwi.
\v 34 Zvino munondinyaradza sei nezvisina maturo, zvamasarirwa nenhema dzega pakupindura kwenyu?
